725556f-a.title: Queens: 64th Street - Catalpa Avenue
725556f-a.text:
64th Street (left foreground), at the S.W, corner of Catalpa Ave.,
showing the home of Henry W. Meyer built by him in the early Nineties.
It was later occupied by the 116th police precinct station of the City
of New York.
March 1923.
View 2: 1922.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
